Notice: We have moved. Our new address is 5500 McNeely Drive, Suite 103

  • Home
  • Bio
  • Practice Areas
  • Links & Resources
  • Contact Us

Call us today:

(919) 836-8076

Are financial fears keeping you awake at night? We often hear that the number one reason for divorce in the United States is conflict over money. Have you been struggling to make ends meet in one household, and wondering how you will be able to survive with the same income stretched over two households? Don’t let fear of the unknown make your situation worse. Call today for a consultation.

Sheryl T. Friedrichs

Attorney and Counselor at Law 

After nineteen years of representing clients in court, she encourages all clients to seek out-of-court solutions  and litigate only as a last resort. 

Call for a consultation to discuss the range of options available to you and the advantages and disadvantages inherent in each process. 

Contact us today for a Consultation

919.836.8076
